{
  "stem": "15694.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the great joy they had when they had eventually a boy, and of course disappointment that he turned out to be a-- what is it?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not retarded-- Down syndrome.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mongoloid.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Down syndrome.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Down syndrome-- that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't love him less.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I called him, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mendele? ?] Yes?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How is everybody?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody gone, except-- and he named two of his sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they came out and invited me, wanted me to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as I say, the next morning with bandaged feet-- I went on the side of my feet-- I went back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the back of the house, there were all these branches.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I selected a stick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people had a smile when I went into the train, walking on the side of my feet and, and with a stick.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyway, I arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got a-- I got a train here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't pay, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no, no money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was no control.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would have found a way on what to say anyway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I arrived there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I reported.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what's going to come now sound-- will sound a bit cozy for [INAUDIBLE] at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of the officers took me by car back into the camp where I could stay in bed, a thing which would be unheard of in later camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For six weeks, I stayed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was-- after three or four weeks, the blisters had, had gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I sort of malingered a bit longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some other fellow was ill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at that time, I remember-- this particular part is not in my book-- I started writing in German, like a fantasy story.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
